an equal education.

00:40:40.180 --> 00:40:44.520
In fact, they are its
most important capital.

00:40:44.520 --> 00:40:46.440
Aside from any
type of technology

00:40:46.440 --> 00:40:48.180
that can be brought
to the island,

00:40:48.180 --> 00:40:49.980
its citizens are
actually the ones

00:40:49.980 --> 00:40:52.140
who are the stewards of
the country and the ones

00:40:52.140 --> 00:40:54.640
that will help us in the future.

00:40:54.640 --> 00:40:57.240
The idea of social
peace in the country

00:40:57.240 --> 00:40:59.340
