00:41:07.990 --> 00:41:11.850
So we would like to also
welcome Google again

00:41:11.850 --> 00:41:16.350
to our coasts to
live out the life

00:41:16.350 --> 00:41:18.960
that Marti had envisioned
through this virtual reality

00:41:18.960 --> 00:41:21.030
that they so graciously
provided us with

00:41:21.030 --> 00:41:22.590
and that they've created.

00:41:22.590 --> 00:41:25.094
